BES · S236 · Patricia Inversion Node · S236 · S236: BES — THE INVERSE OF OVERRIDE

universe of origin : The doorways, bedchambers, and cradles of the common Egyptian home — the dwarf god with lion's mane and grotesque grinning face, who has no temple and no throne, the household protector who frightens off evil not by command but by being loud, ugly, and beloved at the humble margins
seal               : The override is holy precisely because the grinning dwarf at the doorway proves a guardian can protect everything while ranking over nothing.
